{"title":"吹鹿哨　唱新调","authors":["袁袖"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":3,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹鹿哨　唱新调"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁袖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北风吹，雪花飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茫茫大雪没山腰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山下，桦林旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鄂伦春猎队奔山道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老队长把红旗摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在山头吹鹿哨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹着，吹着换了调，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队长的心思谁知道？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘟，嘟，音调躁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年人听着心里跳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鄂家三代吹鹿哨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代更比一代好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧社会，苦难熬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鬼子要把鄂家种根拔掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴安岭上多样宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不许鄂家满山找。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵有鹿肉狐皮貂……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍然穿不暖来吃不饱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一碗肉，一碗酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仇恨肚里咽，热泪滔滔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那年冬天大雪飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天夜晚生二宝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上背，树上吊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鬼子知道可不得了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子过得真快呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转眼二宝长大了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉着他爹的手，抿嘴笑："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我打猎好不好？……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉把胡子翘的高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从肩上摘下鹿哨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿去吧！这只传家宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总有一天你会好好吹鹿哨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉的鹿哨吹的俏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹得青年人捧腹笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人回头叫二宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要接着吹鹿哨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二宝脸红害了臊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们竟拿我开玩笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉看着青年人多骄傲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不吹悲调吹新调。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水也唱呵山也笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨音在兴安岭上呼啸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传家宝传开了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一人一只新鹿哨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨音就是命令号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"獐狍野鹿都报到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴安岭上好猎场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社的猎场有多好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林里出，山里跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各样猎物是社里宝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹着，吹着又换了调，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鄂伦春人的生活好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拆压罗（注），换新房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴皮帽，穿皮袄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹿肉美，狍肉香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜酒一碗人欢笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鄂家三代吹鹿哨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今鹿哨调子妙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鄂伦春人枪法好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪响猎物应声倒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好呵！好呵！猎物真不少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"止不住老汉我心里笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴安岭上红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再吹一曲党和毛主席的好领导。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注：压罗　鄂伦春的帐篷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔赵志方插图〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}